hanks Science!\" is a popular phrase Purple uses for swag and social media. Science isn't expressly stated in our current values; it underlies several of them. As a data professional, that is attractive. I believe in science, I invest in knowledge."), mdx("h2", null, "Tell Me Your Story."), mdx("p", null, "Leaders provide stability in an unstable environment and inspire teams to achieve great things. Embrace values-based leadership to create a culture of trust in your organization, your tribe, from employees to shareholders, better decision-making, greater creativity, and innovation."), mdx("p", null, "We all forget. We all need to be reminded of our purpose. Jamie Dimon once said,"), mdx("br", null), mdx("blockquote", null, mdx("p", {
